# Empty the auto-generated GitHub "Source code (zip/tar.gz)" release archives.
# GitHub builds those from the tag with `git archive`, which honours
# `export-ignore`, so excluding the whole tree leaves those (unremovable) links
# pointing at empty downloads — the source isn't distributed via Releases.
#
# This only affects `git archive` output. `git clone` / `actions/checkout`
# ignore export-ignore, so the CI build still checks out the full source.
* export-ignore
